Thanks for viewing

Feel Free To comment on my profile if you have any questions

This MapPack contains ALL GUNGAME MAPS

gg_battlepyramid	(36 players)

gg_constructcity	(48 players)

gg_kingdom		(50 players)

gg_wundercave 		(40 players)

gg_wunderport_fix 	(32 players)

gg_wundertown 		(48 players)

gg_deadspace_final	(36 players)

in that order



All of these maps have unique features to them

I thought that it would be a better idea to provide all of these in a mappack rather than having people download them one at a time... Enjoy the maps

GG_DEADSPACE_FINAL is one of the maps not featured in the photos.. download the pack to find out what hides inside

Most of these maps include hdr, custom sounds, custom skyboxes, ambient sounds, custom textures, custom models. Sprite effects, advanced geometry, displacement geometry, logic systems, level visual and sound effects, and 6 out of the 7 maps are symmetrical design GG_WUNDERTOWN is isometric
